name:                localize
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            GNU Gettext-based messages localization library
description:         This package provides loader for GNU Gettext .mo (.gmo) files, and API to use
                     them from within Haskell. Unlike original GNU gettext library, this API enables
                     program to change target language at any time - actually, calling code should
                     provide target language at each call of `translate' function, for each string.
